<HL>
   Who's News:
   Bertelsmann AG
</HL>
<DATE>
07/30/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B8
</SO>
<CO>
   WNEWS G.BRT
</CO>
<LP>
   BERTELSMANN AG -- Arlene Friedman was named vice president
and editorial director for the Literary Guild and the
Doubleday Book Club, at Doubleday Book &amp; Music Clubs Inc.
Based in Garden City, N.Y., Doubleday Book &amp; Music Clubs is a
unit of Bertelsmann, a Guetersloh, West Germany, media
company. Effective Aug. 13, Ms. Friedman, previously senior
editor at Crown Publishers Inc., New York, succeeds Maureen
Mahon Egen, who resigned to take another post.
</LP>
