<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
<LP>
   Theodore H. Kruttschnitt, a Burlingame, Calif., investor,
said he acquired a 6.4% stake in Coast Savings Financial
Inc.'s common stock outstanding.
   In a Securities and Exchange Commission filing, Mr.
Kruttschnitt said he holds 976,400 Coast Savings common
shares, all bought May 23 to July 20 for $5.38 to $7.38
apiece.
