controls DWG, NVF and Pennsylvania Engineering, couldn't be
reached for comment.
   A trustee appointed to manage Sharon in January 1988 and
his successor, Mr. Agnew, filed a number of suits and claims
against Mr. Posner and companies he controls involving
alleged excess compensation paid to Mr. Posner by Sharon,
alleged use of Sharon's funds for personal use and other
matters.
