<IN>
EARNINGS (ERN)
PETROLEUM (PET)
OIL, INTEGRATED MAJORS (OIL)
</IN>
<LP>
   Shell Oil Co. reported that second-quarter earnings fell
63% to $161 million from $440 million a year earlier.
   Revenue declined to $5.17 billion from $5.87 billion.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Shell said a major factor in the profit decline was a
